App-bk

A set of command line scripts for recording statistics on
my daily bike rides. This is a work in progress.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc App::bk

Or with the man command.

    man bk

